tiny furniture is a 2010 american independent comedy-drama film written , directed by , and starring lena dunham . the film premiered at south by southwest , where it won the award for best narrative feature , screened at such festivals as maryland film festival , and was released theatrically in the united states on november 12 , 2010 . dunham ’s own mother , the artist laurie simmons , plays aura ’s mother , while her real sister , grace , plays aura ’s on-screen sibling . the actors jemima kirke and alex &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; would also appear in dunham 's television series girls .